<F P=100> Chile </F>
<H3> <TI>   Brazil's Franco Completes Schedule Despite Flu </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PY1103004294 Brasilia Voz do Brasil Network in Portuguese 
2200 GMT 10 Mar 94 </F>

