<H3> <TI>   Activities in Burma Detailed </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  FL1403024894 Havana Tele Rebelde and Cuba Vision Networks in 
Spanish 0100 GMT 14 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL1403024894 </F>
